Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:04.48,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Encounters are mysterious!\NBut cases are even more so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:06.48,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm so glad I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:09.89,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today is the mansion solution!\NThere's more than just a code here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.89,0:00:11.55,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.55,0:00:13.66,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:16.18,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
